cu.explanation_en: Setting Num_Threads_NGAP to 0, which is out of the valid range (typically 1 or more), causing potential thread allocation failures in NGAP processing.

du.explanation_en: Setting Num_Threads_NGAP to 0, which is out of the valid range (typically 1 or more), causing potential thread allocation failures in NGAP processing.
du.explanation_zh: 将 Num_Threads_NGAP 设置为 0，这超出了有效范围（通常为 1 或更多），导致 NGAP 处理中的线程分配失败。
